ry.\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2230, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have done it.\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is an amazing honor, to win the gold medal in the 1,500.\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2308, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an amazing honor\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2271}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was my key target.\\\"\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my key target\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's Jessica Hull won silver in 3:52.56, and Great Britain's Georgia Bell earned bronze in a national record time of 3:52.61.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2333, \"end\": 2342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.8518906155933578, \"rank\": 0.11546303664450472, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2345, \"end\": 2357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Hull\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Hull\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Hull\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Hull\"}, {\"begin\": 2385, \"end\": 2398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9985179141370206, \"rank\": 0.0014820790178336463, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2401, \"end\": 2408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs\", \"score\": 0.990